{"id": "art-25133", "label": "Art. 25133", "title": "Art. 25133", "slug": "art-25133", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_632536367\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1596\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_632536367\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>33</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_574401477\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1595\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_574401477\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Competen&#355;a</span> de verificare\na <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span> fuziunii transfrontaliere sub\naspectul procedurii pe care o urmeaz&#259; societatea participant&#259; la\nfuziune, persoan&#259; juridic&#259; român&#259; sau societate european&#259;\ncu sediul social în România, <span class=SpellE>apar&#355;ine</span>\nregistratorului de la oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\nsau, dup&#259; caz, tribunalului în a c&#259;rui raz&#259; teritorial&#259;\neste situat sediul social al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.\nPrevederile art. 105 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>265/2022</span><span style='color:black'>, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> termenelor de <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;ionare</span>\na cererii, se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor. În scopul exercit&#259;rii\n<span class=SpellE>competen&#355;ei</span> de verificare a <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nfuziunii transfrontaliere, registratorul consult&#259; <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;iile</span>\npublice competente, inclusiv, dac&#259; este cazul, pe cele din statul membru\nal <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante sau\nnou-constituite.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_915637056\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1594\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_915637056\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul în care mai multe <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\nparticipante la fuziune sunt persoane juridice române sau <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\neuropene cu sediul social în România, <span class=SpellE>competen&#355;a</span>\nde verificare a <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span> fuziunii\ntransfrontaliere <span class=SpellE>apar&#355;ine</span> registratorului de la\noficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> sau, dup&#259;\ncaz, tribunalului în a c&#259;rui raz&#259; teritorial&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> are sediul social oricare dintre aceste <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>, care se <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;&#259;</span>\ncu privire la fiecare dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziune.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_816383827\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1593\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_816383827\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Societatea\nparticipant&#259; la fuziune depune, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 84 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </b></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>265/2022</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, la oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\no cerere de eliberare a certificatului prealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere, <span\nclass=SpellE>înso&#355;it&#259;</span> de urm&#259;toarele:</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1453067539\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1592\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1453067539\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)proiectul comun de fuziune transfrontalier&#259;, în\nforma aprobat&#259; de adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> participante la fuziune/<span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> participante la fuziune;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1347790541\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1591\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1347790541\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)raportul administratorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, al\nmembrilor directoratului, la care se anexeaz&#259;, dac&#259; este cazul, <span\nclass=SpellE>observa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> acestora <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cele ale <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau creditorilor cu privire la proiectul\ncomun de fuziune transfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndac&#259; este cazul, opinia <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> acestora <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde raportul prev&#259;zut la art. 251<sup>25</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndup&#259; caz, acordul <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> cu privire la\n<span class=SpellE>renun&#355;area</span> la întocmirea raportului <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau dovezi care s&#259; ateste îndeplinirea <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span> prev&#259;zute la art. 251<sup>25</sup>\nalin. (3) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau alin. (5);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_111605954\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1590\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_111605954\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)raportul expertului independent prev&#259;zut la art. 251<sup>26</sup>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_377556212\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1589\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_377556212\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)hot&#259;rârea adun&#259;rii generale/adun&#259;rilor\ngenerale privind aprobarea fuziunii transfrontaliere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_572756964\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1588\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_572756964\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nîndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> legale referitoare la\nparticiparea <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nla alte <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;i</span> de implicare a acestora,\ninclusiv, dac&#259; este cazul, privind începerea procedurii de negociere,\npotrivit prevederilor Hot&#259;rârii Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>187/2007</span><span style='color:black'>, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu privire la num&#259;rul de <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>\nal fiec&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziune la momentul întocmirii proiectului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_697883455\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1587\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_697883455\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)înscrisuri ce atest&#259; constituirea <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;iilor</span> potrivit proiectului comun de fuziune\ntransfrontalier&#259; sau ca urmare a notific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nde c&#259;tre creditori, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>31</sup> alin. (1), sau, dac&#259; este cazul, <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span>\nconstituite potrivit hot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>\nasupra cererii creditorilor, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nhot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_33547872\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1586\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_33547872\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)înscrisuri ce atest&#259; <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span>\ndisponibilului pentru plata, în termenul legal, a <span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259; este cazul, a <span class=SpellE>compensa&#355;iei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>b&#259;ne&#351;ti</span> stabilite prin hot&#259;râre\njudec&#259;toreasc&#259;, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nhot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1905185387\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1585\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1905185387\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)dac&#259; a fost introdus&#259; o cerere în anulare sau\nde declarare a <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> hot&#259;rârii\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> de aprobare\na fuziunii transfrontaliere, hot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259; prin care\neste respins&#259; cererea, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1824182359\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1584\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1824182359\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)<span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> pe propria\nr&#259;spundere a administratorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, a membrilor\ndirectoratului prin care confirm&#259; c&#259;, potrivit datelor <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nverific&#259;rilor efectuate în baza principiului <span class=SpellE>pruden&#355;ei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>diligen&#355;ei</span>\nbunului administrator, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> financiar&#259;\na <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> participante la fuziune, la\ndata <span class=SpellE>declara&#355;iei</span>, asigur&#259; executarea <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncreditori decurgând din fuziunea transfrontalier&#259;, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>30</sup> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>31</sup>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_365153586\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1583\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_365153586\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Registrul\noficiului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;ine</span>\ndin registrele <span class=SpellE>&#355;inute</span> de acesta <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de la alte <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ii</span>\npublice, pe cale <span class=SpellE>interinstitu&#355;ional&#259;</span>, pe\nbaz&#259; de protocol, dac&#259; este cazul, în scopul verific&#259;rii de\nc&#259;tre registrator a <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nfuziunii transfrontaliere, urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_656772562\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1582\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_656772562\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)certificatul de atestare fiscal&#259;, care s&#259;\nateste executarea <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> participante la fuziune c&#259;tre\nbugetul de stat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> bugetele locale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1506399780\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1581\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1506399780\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din cazierul\nfiscal;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1042488561\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1580\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1042488561\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din cazierul\njudiciar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1931831328\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1579\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1931831328\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din sistemul\ninformatic <span class=SpellE>na&#355;ional</span> integrat de <span\nclass=SpellE>eviden&#355;&#259;</span> a <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;elor</span>\nprovenite din <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span> - ROARMIS;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_871111168\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1578\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_871111168\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nnum&#259;rul de filiale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> amplasarea\ngeografic&#259; a acestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2054778951\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1577\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2054778951\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nnum&#259;rul de <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_280860395\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1576\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_280860395\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind <span\nclass=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunile</span> <span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;ionale</span>\naplicate <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 53 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n54 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>217/2005</span><span style='color:black'>,\nrepublicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 9 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n10 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>467/2006</span><span style='color:black'>, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1830022894\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1575\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1830022894\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din registrul\nbeneficiarilor reali privind beneficiarii reali ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_438047830\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1574\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_438047830\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Dac&#259; procedurile de derulare a fuziunii\ntransfrontaliere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nprivind aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span> nu sunt\nfinalizate ori dac&#259; nu sunt depuse toate înscrisurile prev&#259;zute de <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, registratorul, prin încheiere, în\ntermen de 10 zile de la depunerea cererii, acord&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nun termen pentru regularizare, care nu poate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span>\n15 zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_666321460\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1573\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_666321460\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Dac&#259; toate procedurile de derulare a fuziunii\ntransfrontaliere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nprivind aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span> sunt îndeplinite\npotrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nrapoartele prev&#259;zute la art. 251<sup>25</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n251<sup>26</sup> sunt întocmite potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>,\nregistratorul emite certificatul prealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere, al\nc&#259;rui format se aprob&#259; prin ordin al ministrului <span class=SpellE>justi&#355;iei</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1399665978\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1572\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1399665978\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Registratorul\nrespinge, motivat, cererea de emitere a certificatului prealabil fuziunii\ntransfrontaliere:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1156797904\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1571\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1156797904\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)dac&#259; nu au fost îndeplinite <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;ele</span>\nlegale privind fuziunea transfrontalier&#259;, inclusiv în ceea ce <span\nclass=SpellE>prive&#351;te</span> întocmirea rapoartelor prev&#259;zute la art.\n251<sup>25</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>26</sup>, potrivit <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau\nnu au fost depuse înscrisurile ce atest&#259; îndeplinirea acestor <span\nclass=SpellE>cerin&#355;e</span> legale în termenul acordat de registrator;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2103981096\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1570\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2103981096\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în cazul în care oricare dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziune a fost condamnat&#259; definitiv pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irea</span> unei <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>,\niar pedeapsa amenzii sau, dup&#259; caz, cea complementar&#259; nu a fost\nînc&#259; executat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_688432176\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1569\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_688432176\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Dac&#259; din înscrisurile depuse de societate, din <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nînscrisurile aflate în dosarul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nde la oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> ori din\ncele <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inute</span> de registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\npe cale <span class=SpellE>interinstitu&#355;ional&#259;</span> rezult&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span> unor indicii serioase c&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> transfrontalier&#259; se efectueaz&#259;\nîn scopuri abuzive sau frauduloase, ducând sau <span class=SpellE>propunându-&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; duc&#259; la evaziune sau la eludarea dreptului Uniunii Europene sau a\ncelui intern ori în scopul <span class=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>, registratorul sesizeaz&#259; tribunalul\nîn a c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259;\nsediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, pentru a se <span\nclass=SpellE>pronun&#355;a</span> asupra cererii de emitere a certificatului\nprealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere. În acest caz, toate înscrisurile depuse de\nsocietate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cele <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inute</span>\npe cale <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ional&#259;</span> de oficiul\nregistrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span>\nrelevante din registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> din registrul beneficiarilor reali sunt înaintate <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>\ncompetente.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_45080234\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1568\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_45080234\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Cererea prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (8) este <span\nclass=SpellE>solu&#355;ionat&#259;</span> de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu prec&#259;dere, în camera de consiliu, cu\ncitarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. Pentru termenul fixat\neste citat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> parchetul de pe lâng&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> sesizat&#259;, c&#259;ruia i se\ncomunic&#259;, în copie, înscrisurile din dosar. În acest caz, punerea\nconcluziilor de c&#259;tre procuror este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1586946415\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1567\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1586946415\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Prin hot&#259;rârea <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;at&#259;</span>,\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 527-540 din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>134/2010</span><span style='color:black'> privind </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul de procedur&#259; civil&#259;</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, dac&#259;\nconstat&#259; îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> legale\npentru realizarea fuziunii transfrontaliere, <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\nadmite cererea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dispune emiterea de c&#259;tre\nregistrator a certificatului prealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere. În cazul în\ncare constat&#259; c&#259; fuziunea transfrontalier&#259; se efectueaz&#259; în\nscopuri abuzive sau frauduloase, ducând sau <span class=SpellE>propunându-&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; duc&#259; la înc&#259;lcarea sau la eludarea dreptului Uniunii Europene\nsau a celui intern ori în scopul <span class=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\nrespinge cererea de emitere a certificatului prealabil fuziunii\ntransfrontaliere. Hot&#259;rârea <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> este\nexecutorie <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> este supus&#259; numai apelului,\ncare poate fi exercitat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de Ministerul Public.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1258194802\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1566\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1258194802\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)Termenul de evaluare a cererii de emitere a\ncertificatului prealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere nu poate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span>\n3 luni de la data depunerii acesteia, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span>\ncazului prev&#259;zut la alin. (8), când acesta poate fi prelungit cu cel mult\n3 luni. Dac&#259;, din cauza <span class=SpellE>complexit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nprocedurii transfrontaliere, sunt necesare <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span>\nsau verific&#259;ri suplimentare, iar evaluarea nu poate fi realizat&#259; în\naceste termene, registratorul, din oficiu sau, dup&#259; caz, sesizat de <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;&#259;</span>, comunic&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nparticipante la fuziune motivele eventualelor întârzieri, înainte de expirarea\ntermenelor.</span></p>"}